* ''Salmonella arizonae'' (Borman 1957) Kauffmann 1964，异名
* [[邦戈沙門氏菌|邦戈沙門氏菌]] ''Salmonella bongori'' (Le Minor et al. 1985) Reeves et al. 1989
* [[猪霍乱沙门菌|猪霍乱沙门菌]] ''Salmonella choleraesuis'' corrig. (Smith 1894) Weldin 1927，异名
* [[腸道沙門氏菌|腸道沙門氏菌]] ''Salmonella enterica'' (ex Kauffmann and Edwards 1952) Le Minor and Popoff 1987
* [[肠炎沙门菌|肠炎沙门菌]] ''Salmonella enteritidis'' (Gaertner 1888) Castellani and Chalmers 1919，异名
* [[鸡沙门菌|鸡沙门菌]] ''Salmonella gallinarum''
* [[副伤寒沙门菌|副伤寒沙门菌]] ''Salmonella paratyphi'' (ex Kayser 1902) Ezaki et al. 2000，异名
* [[鸡白痢沙门菌|鸡白痢沙门菌]] ''Salmonella pullorum'' 
* ''Salmonella subterranea'' Shelobolina et al. 2005
* [[伤寒沙门菌|伤寒沙门菌]] ''Salmonella typhi'' (Schroeter 1886) Warren and Scott 1930，异名
* [[鼠伤寒沙门氏菌|鼠伤寒沙门氏菌]] ''Salmonella typhimurium'' (Loeffler 1892) Castellani and Chalmers 1919，异名，鼠伤寒沙门菌 = ''Salmonella enterica''

